metadata.name: Meeting
metadata.description:
She always knew she was special. Today is the first meeting with her true nature - she’s a witch. But it’s up to her - accept this gift or go on living a normal life.

-who are you?
-I’m you
-what does it mean?
-I am your witch nature. I always has been with you. From the very beginning
 ⁃ Why i have never seen you before?
 ⁃ Well, you weren’t ready. But now you can accept me or drive away. What do you choose? 
 ⁃ …(to be continued)
